ProductInfo.Features:
Wide screen, high definition, anti-glare and full color 7" TFT active matrix display;
PAL/NTSC system support, screen ratio 16:9/4:3 adjustable, and brightness, contrast, color adjustable;
2 RCA Video inputs (V1 for DVD player/V2 for Backup camera) and automatically throw-over;
Easy to install with 2 ways available: on car seat headrest with headrest shroud, or on dashboard with the stand;
Available for car VCD, DVD, GPS, etc. and especially designed to connect to your car camera.
